import React from 'react'
import ReviewRestaurantForm from '../components/ReviewRestaurantForm'
import ReviewRatingStars from '../components/ReviewRatingStars'
import ReviewCards from '../components/ReviewCards'
import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'

const ReviewRestaurantPage = () => {

  return (
    <section className='review-section'>
      <ReviewRestaurantForm />
      <ReviewRatingStars rating={2.5} />
      <ReviewCards />      
    </section>    
  )
}

export default ReviewRestaurantPage
